{
  "$meta": {
    "name": "Aham UI",
    "version": "7.0.1",
    "basis": "Claude desktop temperament — minimal, restrained, whitespace-first",
    "lineage": "Regularized from the Aham Workbench design system. Two changes: accent terracotta → blue #336EE8; fonts unified to one sans (Inter + YaHei/SimHei) + mono, serif dropped; CJK fallback added. All other values faithful to Workbench.",
    "principles": [
      "necessity first (default is don't-add)",
      "blue is a garnish not a fill",
      "hierarchy from background tiers + whitespace, never shadow/color",
      "status = symbol + color dual channel, never a block",
      "flat — no resting shadows"
    ],
    "tracks": "v6.0 起 Aham 落地分四轨,布局心智不同,须分轨制定(见 track / breakpoint / contentWidth / grid):网页轨(居中收口+12栅格+rem断点,再分桌面/移动) · 应用轨(macOS,左对齐铺满+展开pane+dp断点派生) · Office轨(Word流式/Excel网格/PPT画布三子模型) · 邮件轨(table+600px)。结构↔业内(Material/Carbon/Ant/Fluent/HIG 等),取值全用 Aham。",
    "note": "v6.1: 第 2 层新增 2.9 媒体与对话(纳入自 AhamVoice 的 9 个招牌件:player/transcript+speaker-marker/prose/composer/attachment/avatar/sidebar__*/auth-shell/form-section),CSS 进 aham-ui.css 第 9 节;新增 avatar 尺寸档 token;说话人标记用形状不用颜色(守铁律);全景展示页重建为手写版。纯追加,八层结构不动。v6.0: 新增页面布局体系(第 8 层)——多轨页面骨架/页型(Canonical Layouts)/页眉/搜索筛选/状态(空·加载·错误·骨架)/预览模式/内容密度/容器查询/弹窗按钮顺序/i18n-RTL布局/z-index阶梯/打印,补齐两轮调研(Apple HIG + 业内横扫)缺口约 22 项;断点改为网页 rem 为单一事实源、应用 dp 派生(废止 v5 的 sm380/md860/lg1280)。v5.1: 清理 15 个旧/重复类。v5.0: 对照 Apple HIG 完整性审计补全 30 项。v4.0: 以 Apple HIG 框架重构。"
  },
